metadata.name: Pixel Seoul Land
metadata.description:
This work expresses Seoul in Korea with a pixel island.

It contains the bright lights and energy of Seoul at night.
Haetae, which appears with firecrackers, lights up and protects the entire city.


It used various landmarks in Seoul, including Namsan Tower, Gwanghwamun, Myeongdong Cathedral, Han River, DDP, Lotte Tower&World, 63 Building, National Assembly Building, World Cup Park, and SEOUL sculptures.
